Published Time: 2023-06-12T06:07:13+08:00

Description: China has the world's largest and highly militarized maritime police fleet. It is aggressive in regional disputes, leading to neighboring countries to upgrade maritime police forces. The maritime police of Asian countries have become more and more like navy and become pioneers of regional competition. Ted Aljobe/Age France-Presse-Getty Images April, near the South China Sea Dispute Island Reef, the Philippine Coast Guard personnel passed by an inflatable boat from an inflatable boat.

